sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / API Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as TrainJob Reconciler<br/>trainer-controller-manager
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod (rank-0)<br/>28080/TCP HTTP
    participant WorkerPods as Training Worker Pods

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User, Controller: Flow 1: TrainJob Creation & Resource Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, TLS Client Cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (Allow/Deny)
        K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob Created
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event (TrainJob)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create JobSet<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy (RHOAI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PodGroup (if Volcano/CoScheduling)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create SSH Secret + Hostfile CM (if MPI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Controller, TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking (RHOAI)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: List Pods (APIReader direct call)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list with rank-0 IP
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy enforced)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Metrics JSON (loss, epoch, step)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Patch TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(224, 255, 230)
        Note over TrainingPod, WorkerPods: Flow 3: Distributed PyTorch Training
        WorkerPods->>TrainingPod: Connect to master<br/>29500/TCP plaintext
        TrainingPod-->>WorkerPods: Coordination response
        WorkerPods->>WorkerPods: NCCL all-reduce<br/>Dynamic ports, TCP plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy: same-job pods only
    end

    rect rgb(255, 224, 230)
        Note over TrainingPod, WorkerPods: Flow 4: MPI Distributed Training
        TrainingPod->>WorkerPods: SSH Launch (mpirun)<br/>2222/TCP SSH, ECDSA P521 key auth
        WorkerPods->>WorkerPods: MPI/NCCL communication<br/>Dynamic ports, TCP plaintext<br/>NetworkPolicy: same-job pods only
    end
